Various packages: 

* EasyPG (used by Gnus)
* S/MIME (GnusSMIME, ExtendSMIME)
* DefaultEncrypt
* Mailcrypt (BbdbAndMailCrypt)
* bbdb-pgp.el (part of BbdbMode)
* mc-bbdb.el
* PGG (GnusPGG)
* WlSigningMails for signing mails in WanderLust.
* EncryptingAttachments for encrypting attached file using detached signatures.
* [[Gmail, Gnus and GPG]]
